description:
We provide one of the best selections of used and new cars. Our top rated auto service department provides service for the Berkeley community.

We work hard to get you into the vehicle you always wanted. That new car, SUV, or truck is waiting for you, and we work with a broad spectrum of lenders to make sure you will get the most complete and beneficial financial package available in Berkeley.
